node.title: Child dies in Auckland 'water-related' incident
node.description: Emergency services were called to a Papatoetoe address around 5.15pm. The child was taken to hospital in a critical condition but died a short time later.
node.content:
["A child has died in "water-related" incident in Auckland, police say.", "", "
File image Photo: 123rf
", "Emergency services were called to a Papatoetoe address around 5.15pm.", "The child was taken to hospital in a critical condition but died a short time later, police said.", "Police are making enquiries on behalf of the coroner."]
